trans-unit.source: Converts service, contract, and endpoint information into metadata documents.
trans-unit.target: Convierte el servicio, el contrato y la información del extremo en documentos de metadatos.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter> class to transform <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription> or <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint> objects into metadata represented by <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSection> objects.
trans-unit.target: Utilice la clase <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter> para transformar <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription> o los objetos <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint> en los metadatos representados por los objetos <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSection>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter> is used in a three-step process.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter> se utiliza en un proceso de tres pasos.

trans-unit.source: Call the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportContract%2A>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoint%2A>, or <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoints%2A> method, passing the appropriate parameters.
trans-unit.target: Llame al método <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportContract%2A>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoint%2A>, o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.ExportEndpoints%2A>, pasando los parámetros adecuados.

trans-unit.source: Determine whether there are any export errors by checking the base <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataExporter.Errors%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Compruebe la propiedad <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataExporter.Errors%2A> base para determinar si se han producido errores de exportación.

trans-unit.source: If there are no errors, use the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.GetGeneratedMetadata%2A> to get a collection of <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSection> objects or get more specific versions of the metadata using the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.GeneratedWsdlDocuments%2A> or <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.GeneratedXmlSchemas%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Si no hay ningún error, utilice <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.GetGeneratedMetadata%2A> para obtener una colección de los objetos <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.MetadataSection> o versiones más específicas de los metadatos mediante las propiedades <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.GeneratedWsdlDocuments%2A> o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlExporter.GeneratedXmlSchemas%2A>.

trans-unit.source: You can support exporting custom WSDL extensions by implementing the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension> interface and custom policy assertions by implementing the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IPolicyExportExtension> interface.
trans-unit.target: Es compatible exportar las extensiones WSDL personalizadas mediante la implementación de la interfaz <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension>, y personalizar las aserciones de la directiva mediante la interfaz <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IPolicyExportExtension>.

trans-unit.source: For details, see the documentation for those interfaces.
trans-unit.target: Para obtener más información, vea la documentación de dichas interfaces.

trans-unit.source: The `WsdlExporter` can only be used to export metadata from `ContractDescription` instances that contain Common Language Runtime (CLR) type information, such as a `ContractDescription` instance created using the `ContractDescription.GetContract` method or created as part of the `ServiceDescription` for a `ServiceHost` instance.
trans-unit.target: `WsdlExporter` sólo puede utilizarse para exportar los metadatos desde las instancias `ContractDescription` que contienen el tipo de información Common Language Runtime (CLR), por ejemplo, una instancia `ContractDescription` creada mediante el método `ContractDescription.GetContract`, o como parte de `ServiceDescription` para una instancia `ServiceHost`.

trans-unit.source: You cannot use the `WsdlExporter` to export metadata from `ContractDescription` instances imported from service metadata or constructed without type information.
trans-unit.target: No puede utilizar `WsdlExporter` para exportar metadatos a partir de las instancias `ContractDescription` importadas desde los metadatos del servicio o construidas sin información del tipo.
